<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;1,600&family=PT+Sans+Narrow:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%include header.ejs%>
    <div class="banner corporate"></div>
    <div class="article">
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial__quote">
              Arceus executed a sophisticated and complex intelligence operation that eventually led to the dismissal of the arbitration proceedings
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial__author">
              <img src="/images/forbes.png">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-watermark">
            <img src="/images/suited-man.png">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <h3 class="article__title">Corporate</h3>
          <p class="para-block">We at Arceus Consulting equip corporates with knowledge, strategies, and advanced tools that empower them in facing challenging scenarios in rapidly transforming business environments. Our experienced team of consultants provides robust due diligence, analysis, and investigative services that help corporates make critical decisions during mergers and acquisitions, keep track of the competition, and evaluate potential business partnerships.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-dual">
        <img src="../images/corporate-break-1.jpeg">
        <img src="../images/corporate-break-3.jpeg">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Competitive Intelligence</p>
          <p class="para-block">
            Arceus Consulting specialises in providing comprehensive due diligence services for M&A, investments, competition strategy, and new business partnerships. Leveraging our core strength in digital and cyber, we help clients by collecting and analysing intelligence that enable them to better navigate challenges in their business’ environment.
            <ul>
              <li>We identify potential counterparty risks in M&A deals through our advanced research and cyber capabilities.</li>
              <li>We provide intelligence on issues of corruption, source of wealth, poor commercial track record, and integrity/reputational issues, which have critical implications.</li>
              <li>We provide competitive intelligence regarding competition’s strategies, R&D plans, new products and services, and unrevealed usable leverage points of conflicts, corruption, fraud, or bribery.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="para-title">Deep Level Due Diligence</p>
          <p class="para-block">Due diligence is a vital tool that corporates must deploy while assessing potential business partners and making critical decisions. Arceus Consulting provides Deep Level Due Diligence services for supporting corporate risk management. We provide intelligence to our clients for decisions involving investments, mergers and acquisitions, legal mandates, hiring, and more. We deep dive into multiple digital sources using our digital and social engineering expertise   to assess critical parameters of target companies and their stakeholders. We help to identify the target’s motives and interests, past behaviour in other roles, and any additional information that could reveal behaviour of critical importance.
          </p>
          <p class="para-title">Mergers and Acquisitions</p>
          <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting provides exclusive research and due diligence services to corporates for Mergers and Acquisitions, investments, and assessment of management teams. We take due diligence a step further by incorporating our cyber expertise with digital technologies for assessing, managing, and mitigating risks in high-profile deals. We gather digital evidence through cyber techniques and social engineering to identify legal risks, assess compliance issues, find employee misconduct, and mitigate threatening individuals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-single">
        <img src="../images/corporate-break-2.jpeg">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Methodology and Techniques</p>
          <p class="para-block">
            <ul>
              <li>Assessing court records — criminal, civil, or other</li>
              <li>Social media assessment</li>
              <li>Global searches</li>
              <li>Business and property records</li>
              <li>Social Engineering</li>
              <li>Open Source and Dark web Cyber probing</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting provides specialized due diligences services to corporates in the following parameters:</p>
          <p class="para-block">Threat Analysis of Key Individuals:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Mitigating threatening individuals</li>
            <li>Identifying employee misconduct</li>
            <li>Assessing workplace misconduct and violence</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="para-block">Compliance Assessment of Target Companies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Know Your Customer (KYC) business-to-business check and vendor screening</li>
            <li>Civil and criminal cases at the local and federal level</li>
            <li>Anti-money laundering checks</li>
            <li>Assessment of political exposure</li>
            <li>Anti-bribery and corruption assessment</li>
            <li>Corporate disputes</li>
            <li>Fraud identification</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="para-block">Reputation Management:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Checks on close business associates, JV partners, and commercial agents</li>
            <li>Business integrity concerns</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <li>Investments of target companies</li>
            <li>Pre-merger and acquisition transactions</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="para-title">Money Embezzlement and Kickbacks</p>
          <p class="para-block">Frauds such as embezzlements and kickbacks can cause virulent downturns for organizations leading to severe crises. Disruptions caused by such events have the potential to shake customer and stakeholder confidence. Arceus Consulting provides specialized services for risk management. We provide clients with a clear assessment of their exposure and devise actionable plans to prevent potentially catastrophic repercussions. We deploy our digital capabilities and cyber forensics expertise to help clients protect themselves and recover from crises.
            <ul>
              <li>Uncover Fraud</li>
              <li>Address Economic and Financial Crimes</li>
              <li>Manage Disputes and Crises</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="para-title">Strategy and Leadership Mapping</p>
          <p class="para-block">Mapping the strategy and plans of competition is a vital tool for corporates. Arceus Consulting derives key strategy elements and plans of our client’s competition through cyber forensics by conducting in-depth research using our proprietary digital tools and cyber expertise. We assess important leadership profiles, including executives and members of the board of directors, to understand their interests, motivations, strategies, and personal circumstances.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Internal Fraud and Misrepresentation</p>
          <p class="para-block">Corporates constantly need to be vigilant towards identifying and mitigating risks arising from internal frauds such as financial frauds, conflicting managerial interests, or misrepresentation. We at Arceus Consulting deploy our digital capabilities to collect information using a wide variety of techniques. From cyber evidence gathering and social engineering to deep forensic accounting skills coupled with our global linguistic and cultural knowledge, we can serve our clients in multiple business jurisdictions over the world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
  <%include footer.ejs%>
</html>
